'''Lindsay Duncan''' (born [[November 7]], [[1950s#1950|1950]]) is a Scottish actress who voiced [[TC-14]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''The Phantom Menace'']]. Her husband, [[Hilton McRae]], played [[Arvel Crynyd]] in [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Return of the Jedi'']].<ref name="100 Scenes">''[[Star Wars in 100 Scenes]]''</ref>

